annotationA: YKT6 v-SNARE; SNAP receptor activity; protein-cysteine S-palmitoyltransferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: retrograde vesicle-mediated transport, Golgi to ER; vesicle-mediated transport; ER to Golgi vesicle-mediated transport; Belongs to the synaptobrevin family
annotationB: Vesicle transport protein USE1; SNARE that may be involved in targeting and fusion of Golgi-derived retrograde transport vesicles with the ER (By similarity). Required for protein secretion
